00:46.755 --> 00:49.307
I've never been through this.
I don't know how to act.

00:49.924 --> 00:52.602
All I know is that I gotta
get out of here for a while.

00:53.178 --> 00:54.562
<i>Meaning what?</i>

00:54.971 --> 00:58.409
Meaning I gotta figure out what
the hell I'm doing with my life.

00:58.433 --> 00:59.952
I can't do it here.

00:59.976 --> 01:02.070
So I'm gonna take off
for a little while.

01:03.063 --> 01:04.781
