03:53.316 --> 03:54.251
You made me lose count.

03:54.275 --> 03:55.628
Fifteen years?

03:55.652 --> 03:58.329
That doesn't strike
you as a little...

03:58.446 --> 03:59.840
Okay, so it's a little unusual,

03:59.864 --> 04:02.041
