hour before the ceremony?

05:38.629 --> 05:40.264
What do I think?

05:40.339 --> 05:43.360
Well, assuming the bride was...

05:43.384 --> 05:44.403
Perfect.

05:44.427 --> 05:48.657
Yeah. Well, that's
pretty unforgivable.

05:48.681 --> 05:51.442
That's what I think too.

06:37.021 --> 06:38.082
Is anybody at your house?

06:38.106 --> 06:39.124
