06:39.148 --> 06:40.741
No one.

06:42.068 --> 06:43.828
She really knew Kennedy?

06:44.403 --> 06:47.132
Man, I've never really known
people who knew people before.

06:47.156 --> 06:49.426
Well, don't be intimidated. She
really likes you, I can tell.

06:49.450 --> 06:51.419
