07:24.026 --> 07:25.796
You can't blame me for being
a little cautious here.

07:25.820 --> 07:27.589
That is not fair. I apologized.

07:27.613 --> 07:28.632
I know.

07:28.656 --> 07:31.510
It's just silly little things,
stupid little things,

07:31.534 --> 07:34.295
like trust and total
devotion, take time.

07:34.454 --> 07:36.297
Okay? Understand?

07:36.914 --> 07:38.799
Yeah. I understand.

07:42.587 --> 07:44.346
I hate it, but I understand.

08:02.857 --> 08:04.334
Nice, don't you think?

08:04.358 --> 08:06.128
Whatever.

08:06.152 --> 08:07.296
Yes?

08:07.320 --> 08:09.497
Salinger. I have a reservation.

08:10.031 --> 08:12.384
