snakes and rodents,

08:32.553 --> 08:34.405
but when it comes to bugs,

08:34.429 --> 08:36.440
I'm... I'm...

08:37.850 --> 08:40.568
I'm Courtney. Hi.

08:41.020 --> 08:44.082
I'm sorry. I'm Charlie.

08:44.106 --> 08:46.001
Here you go, Mr. Salinger.

08:46.025 --> 08:47.701
The honeymoon suite.

08:49.570 --> 08:50.797
You're Charlie Salinger,

08:50.821 --> 08:52.382
and you're on your
honeymoon, so I'm...

08:52.406 --> 08:53.467
No, I'm not.

08:53.491 --> 08:55.417
I'm with my sister.

08:55.535 --> 08:57.346
Right. Okay.

08:57.370 --> 08:59.463
No, really. She's 12.

08:59.497 --> 09:02.476
And she kind of
hates me right now,

09:02.500 --> 09:04.134
