10:39.847 --> 10:41.815
Yeah. Cosmopolitan even.

10:42.391 --> 10:43.910
So does that work for you?

10:43.934 --> 10:46.153
Yeah. Sure. Why not?

10:46.437 --> 10:47.780
Okay.

10:47.980 --> 10:50.500
