12:03.389 --> 12:05.399
My father tells me.

12:05.599 --> 12:07.077
Who's your father?

12:07.101 --> 12:09.528
Juan Carlos Sabato Luis Sanchez.

12:09.812 --> 12:11.331
This is his hotel.

12:11.355 --> 12:13.949
The best hotel in all
