15:14.955 --> 15:17.299
I'm here to fool around.

15:27.343 --> 15:28.810
What does it mean?

15:29.219 --> 15:30.739
What did he mean
when he wrote this?

15:30.763 --> 15:33.357
Sweetheart, maybe we should
discuss this in private.

15:33.724 --> 15:35.660
Yeah. Look, I should...

15:35.684 --> 15:37.444
No. I have no problem
with Bailey hearing.

15:37.561 --> 15:38.580
Sarah, I really...

15:38.604 --> 15:40.332
Just stay here!

15:40.356 --> 15:42.334
Is Dad not my father?

15:42.358 --> 15:44.544
Did you get pregnant
with someone else?

15:44.568 --> 15:46.129
