baby Sarah that died

15:46.153 --> 15:47.714
that you named me after?

15:47.738 --> 15:49.706
Am I adopted? What are
we talking about here?

15:51.700 --> 15:53.252
Yes.

15:53.535 --> 15:54.471
Yes, what?

15:54.495 --> 15:56.630
